    <title>Nginx服务安装SSL证书</title>
    <url>/2020/07/13/Nginx%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85SSL%E8%AF%81%E4%B9%A6/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://tangxiaoyan.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/tuchuang/u=3379754713,1922618047&fm=26&gp=0.jpg" alt=""></p>
<p>本篇内容用来讲述如何配置Nginx，为服务器安装SSL证书，完成网页通过https的访问。<a id="more"></a></p>
<h2 id="前提条件"><a href="#前提条件" class="headerlink" title="前提条件"></a>前提条件</h2><ul>
<li><p>准备文件远程传输软件，例如Xftp，WinSCP，FinalShell等（建议从官网下载最新版本）</p>
</li>
<li><p>准备远程登录工具，例如FinalShell，Xshell等（建议从官网下载最新版本）</p>
</li>
<li><p>配置好服务器，并已在当前服务器中安装配置 Nginx 服务。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="申请SSL证书"><a href="#申请SSL证书" class="headerlink" title="申请SSL证书"></a>申请SSL证书</h2><p>去各大平台申请SSL证书如阿里云、华为云、腾讯云，这里我选择华为云。</p>
<p>在购买ssl产品前，一定要先详细了解各类型ssl产品，根据自己的公司的类型，选择适合的ssl证书类型</p>
<p>SSL证书一般分为EV型、OV型、DV型三种类型的证书。</p>
<p>EV型SSL证书适用：金融（银行、基金、证券、保险）、互联网金融（P2P、基金代销、众筹、融资、投资、理财类）及对安全性标准要求较高的行业。</p>
<p>OV型SSL证书适用：互联网信息、电子商务、制造行业、运营商、政府、教育等行业。</p>
<p>DV型SSL证书适用：小型客户、个人及测试使用。</p>
<p>这里我在华为云选择申请免费的DV型证书。</p>
<p><img src="https://tangxiaoyan.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/tuchuang/20200713225832.png" alt=""></p>
<h2 id="下载SSL证书，并上传至服务器"><a href="#下载SSL证书，并上传至服务器" class="headerlink" title="下载SSL证书，并上传至服务器"></a>下载SSL证书，并上传至服务器</h2><p>申请成功之后我们需要下载证书到本地，因为我们是通过Nginx服务，所以只解压Nginx文件夹内的证书。</p>
<p><img src="https://tangxiaoyan.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/tuchuang/20200713230109.png" alt=""></p>
<p>解压完成后可以看到两个文件，我们需要把这两个文件上传至自己的服务器。</p>
<p><img src="https://tangxiaoyan.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/tuchuang/20200713230312.png" alt=""></p>
<p>在Nginx的主目录，创建一个叫做cert的目录，通过Xftp把上面两个文件传输至此文件夹内。</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir /etc/nginx/cert</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="https://tangxiaoyan.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/tuchuang/20200713230503.png" alt=""></p>
<h2 id="修改Nginx的默认配置"><a href="#修改Nginx的默认配置" class="headerlink" title="修改Nginx的默认配置"></a>修改Nginx的默认配置</h2><ul>
<li>打开Nginx的配置文件</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim /etc/nginx/nginx.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>修改Nginx的配置文件为如下，80端口的http服务不需要做更改，把下面代码加入到80端口前面。</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">server &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    listen       443 ssl http2 default_server;</span><br><span class="line">    listen       [::]:443 ssl http2 default_server;</span><br><span class="line">    server_name  www.tangxiaoyani.com;</span><br><span class="line">    root         /home/hexoBlog;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    ssl_certificate <span class="string">"/etc/nginx/cert/server.crt"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    ssl_certificate_key <span class="string">"/etc/nginx/cert/server.key"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    ssl_session_cache shared:SSL:1m;</span><br><span class="line">    ssl_session_timeout  10m;</span><br><span class="line">    ssl_ciphers ECDHE-RSA-AES128-GCM-SHA256:ECDHE:ECDH:AES:HIGH:!NULL:!aNULL:!MD5:!ADH:!RC4;</span><br><span class="line">    ssl_prefer_server_ciphers on;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># Load configuration files for the default server block.</span></span><br><span class="line">    include /etc/nginx/default.d/*.conf;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    location / &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    error_page 404 /404.html;</span><br><span class="line">        location = /40x.html &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    error_page 500 502 503 504 /50x.html;</span><br><span class="line">        location = /50x.html &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="https://tangxiaoyan.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/tuchuang/20200713231602.png" alt=""></p>
<p>OK，这样https的网页就配置好了，最后我们设置80端口的http服务，这样可以完成如果有人通过http服务访问网页会强制跳转到https页面。</p>
<h2 id="设置http强制跳转https"><a href="#设置http强制跳转https" class="headerlink" title="设置http强制跳转https"></a>设置http强制跳转https</h2><p>设置非常简单，只需要添加一行代码，但是需要记住，https的代码要写在http的上面。</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rewrite ^(.*)$ https://<span class="variable">$host</span><span class="variable">$1</span> permanent;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<p><img src="https://tangxiaoyan.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/tuchuang/20200713232219.png" alt=""></p>
]]></content>
