    <title>windows实验</title>
    <url>/2020/07/18/windows%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Windows实验"><a href="#Windows实验" class="headerlink" title="Windows实验"></a>Windows实验</h1><p><img src="https://tangxiaoyan.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/tuchuang/213.jpg" alt=""></p>
<p><strong>实验目的，搭建故障转移群集，把web与FTP服务的物理目录存放在故障转移服务器上，断开其中一个故障转移节点，验证能否访问web域ftp。</strong></p>
<a id="more"></a>

<p><strong>实验环境</strong></p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>主机名</th>
<th>IP</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>S4-域控</td>
<td>192.168.128.30/24</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>S5-节点</td>
<td>192.168.128.31/24   192.168.3.2/24   192.168.4.2/24</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>S6 -节点</td>
<td>192.168.128.32/24   192.168.3.3/24   192.168.4.3/24</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>S10-文件</td>
<td>192.168.4.4/24</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<p><strong>设置 S4的IP地址。</strong></p>
<img src="https://tangxiaoyan.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/tuchuang/image-20200717142232212.png" style="zoom:50%;" />

<p><strong>关机状态为S5、S6添加两张网卡，并设置好各个网卡的IP地址，这里需要我设置的IP比较多，而且虚拟机过多导致我电脑很卡就不逐个截图。</strong></p>
<p><img src="https://tangxiaoyan.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/tuchuang/image-20200717142745304.png" style="zoom: 33%;" /><img src="https://tangxiaoyan.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/tuchuang/20200717144008.png" alt=""></p>
<p><strong>设置S10的IP地址</strong></p>
<img src="https://tangxiaoyan.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/tuchuang/20200717143435.png" style="zoom: 80%;" />



<p> 在S4创建域2020kk.com环境并升级为域控，创建用户user1,user2。A2，A3加入到域中。</p>
<p><strong>为S4安装域服务。</strong></p>
<img src="https://tangxiaoyan.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/tuchuang/20200717144843.png" style="zoom:50%;" />

<p><strong>设置S4为域控</strong></p>
<img src="https://tangxiaoyan.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/tuchuang/20200717145011.png" style="zoom:50%;" />

<p><strong>根据题目要求设置域名为2020kk.com</strong></p>
<img src="https://tangxiaoyan.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/tuchuang/20200717145248.png" style="zoom:50%;" />

<p><strong>域安装成功之后，把S5和S6加入域，并创建两个用户</strong></p>
